Installation & Setup
1️⃣ Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/ombakle/MineBot-An-Intelligent-AI-Powered-Chatbot-to-Simplify-Mining-Regulations-and-Safety-Compliance.git
cd MineBot-An-Intelligent-AI-Powered-Chatbot-to-Simplify-Mining-Regulations-and-Safety-Compliance

2️⃣ Create Virtual Environment
python -m venv venv

Activate it:
Windows
venv\Scripts\activate
Mac/Linux
source venv/bin/activate

3️⃣ Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

4️⃣ Run Data Processing (Optional)

If you want to regenerate the knowledge base:
python preprocess.py
python qa_generator.py

5️⃣ Run the Application
python app.py

6️⃣ Open in Browser
http://127.0.0.1:5000/
